<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa gen ka za'i,
 &quot;Na hatna a tawm hi;
 Kivengin paucham in,
 Na bangkim keiah mu'n.

[V2]
 Isu'n A din tai,
 A kawmah ka ba'i;
 Ka gitlohna ni'n cheng chuh,
 Vuk bangin a sawp vam.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa tuhin ka mu'i,
 Nangmah theihna maiin;
 Pha'kna a hihdam thei,
 Lunggil khauh a hih nem.

[V4]
 3. Thilpha him ka nei puoi,
 Nei lungsiet theih nadi'n;
 Ka puon haw sawp vam ka,
 Belam No thisan in.

[V5]
 4. Ka thagau tatsa chuh,
 Than apat a thawh tieng;
 &quot;Isu'n A din vek tai&quot;
 Ti'n kipak zing tana.

[V6]
 5. Van Lalchutphah ma ah,
 Bukim a ka din tieng;
 Ka zawhna cheng ngang ka,
 Lal Isu kengbul ah.</lyrics>
<title>ALL TO CHRIST I OWE</title>
</song>